This Repository contains some of my config files for the applications
I'm using, aka dotfiles. Mind most of them start with a dot, so you
might need to use ls -a or something similiar to see them.

The .zshrc and .vimrc are heavily based on the versions used in GRML,
www.grml.org - Thanks!

